<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Page Not Found Â· Blockster</title>
    <style>
      * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
        background: #F5F6FB;
        color: #141414;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 2rem;
      }
      .container {
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 480px;
      }
      .logo {
        height: 28px;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
      }
      .code {
        font-size: 6rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: #CAFC00;
        line-height: 1;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 #141414;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      }
      p {
        color: #6B7280;
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #141414;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
        border-radius: 100px;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        transition: background 0.2s;
      }
      .btn:hover { background: #333; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/"><img src="https://ik.imagekit.io/blockster/blockster-logo.png" alt="Blockster" class="logo" /></a>
      <div class="code">404</div>
      <h1>Page not found</h1>
      <p>This page doesn't exist or may have been moved. Head back to the homepage to find the latest articles and content.</p>
      <a href="/" class="btn">Back to Homepage</a>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
